Ho Ho Hooo! It s LiveBoard Claus and I have brought some new features for my beloved users! Now you have a brand new image editing panel which will allow you to crop duplicate delete and apply the inserted image with a single click. In addition to this adding and navigating through the pages became much easier with the new design. Merry Christmas Happy New Year!

Hey did you hear that click sound ! It was a graph created by our newly integrated Graph editor powered by Desmos the best graphing tool out there. Now our users will be able to plot equations and insert graphs into LiveBoard with a single click.
